data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Del Webb Naples, Ave Maria! This stunning single-family home offers the perfect blend of luxury and comfort. The tile flooring throughout adds a touch of elegance, while the corner lot location provides privacy and tranquility. The exquisite granite countertops that grace the kitchen and bathrooms, adding a touch of sophistication to every space. The brushed nickel hardware adds a modern and sleek touch to the home, with upgraded 8' doors. The tray ceiling in the primary bedroom adds a touch of architectural beauty, while the plantation shutters and crown moulding throughout the home adds a touch of elegance. The whole house fabric storm screens provide peace of mind during stormy weather, while the extended lanai is perfect for outdoor entertaining. And to top it all off, this home features a brand new HVAC system with UV and air purification, ensuring a comfortable and healthy living environment. The garage includes heavy duty storage racks and a "lifestyle" full garage door screen.  This home checks boxes!  Ave Maria is a golf cart friendly town with shopping, restaurants, parks and year round events.  A social membership is included to the club.
